{"word":"G1983 - ἐπισκοπέω - episkopéō - ep-ee-skop-eh'-o - Look diligently","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπισκοπέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">episkopéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-skop-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Look diligently</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - எச்சரிக்கையாயிரு, மேய்"},{"paragraph":"to look upon, inspect, oversee, look after, care for"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G4648 - σκοπέω - skopéō - skop-eh'-o/4648\">G4648</a>; to <i>oversee</i>; by implication to <i>beware:</i> - look diligently, take the oversight.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1980/1980\">G1980</a>, <a href=\"#/G1983/1983\">G1983</a>, <a href=\"#/G1984/1984\">G1984</a>, <a href=\"#/G244/244\">G244</a>"}]}